XianhaiHuangistheDeputyDirectorofCenterforReserchonRegionalEconomyOpeninganddevelopment(REOD),ZhejiangUniversity.
&nbsp;
ProfessorXianhaiHuang'sresearchfieldisInternationalEconomicsandDevelopmentEconomics.HispublicationsincludeLeapfrogging-orientedEconomicGrowth:DevelopingPathsoftheBackwardCountriesandChina&rsquo;sChoiceandothersevenco-workpapers.Hehadpublishedmorethat50papersinEconomicResearchJournal,ManagementWorldandsoon.&nbsp;
